Image: Kuli Roberts By Andile Mngxitama The passing on of Kuli Roberts has affected me in ways I didn’t anticipate. I will write a tribute to the “insider, outsider”, a hybrid between mabrrr and the ungovernability of Jabu Pule at his peak. These are epoch making personalities.They reflect an era in all its frailties. Hamba Kahle sisiwethu! Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization.